heading: 2. The 1st day of March 2023 is appointed to be the establishment day for
text_raw:
2. The 1st day of March 2023 is appointed to be the establishment day for 

the purposes of the Tailte Éireann Act 2022 (No. 50 of 2022). 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

21 February, 2023. 

DARRAGH O’BRIEN, 

Minister for Housing, Local Government and Heritage. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 24th February, 2023.

EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation.) 

This Order provides that 1 March 2023 is the establishment day for the 
purposes of the Tailte Éireann Act 2022 (No. 50 of 2022).
